cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper deals with anomaly detection in images using deep transfer learning with convolutional neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves the use of neural networks, which could also place it in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves the use of data analysis techniques, which could also place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
